        when multiplication_direct_0 =>
            -- -- In case of size 1
            -- reg_a = a0_X; reg_b = b0_X; reg_acc = 0; o0_X = reg_o; o1_X = reg_o >> 272; Enable sign a,b; operation : a*b + acc;
            next_sm_free_flag <= '0';
            next_sm_rotation_size <= "11";
            next_sm_circular_shift_enable <= '1';
            next_sel_address_a <= '0';
            next_sel_address_b_prime <= "00";
            next_sm_specific_carmela_address_a <= "000";
            next_sm_specific_carmela_address_b <= "000";
            next_sm_specific_carmela_address_o <= "000";
            next_sm_specific_carmela_next_address_o <= "001";
            next_carmela_enable_signed_a <= '1';
            next_carmela_enable_signed_b <= '1';
            next_carmela_sel_load_reg_a <= "00";
            next_carmela_clear_reg_b <= '0';
            next_carmela_clear_reg_acc <= '1';
            next_carmela_sel_shift_reg_o <= '0';
            next_carmela_enable_update_reg_s <= '0';
            next_carmela_sel_reg_s_reg_o_sign <= '0';
            next_carmela_reg_s_reg_o_positive <= '0';
            next_sm_sign_a_mode <= '0';
            next_sm_carmela_operation_mode <= "10";
            next_carmela_enable_reg_s_mask <= '0';
            next_carmela_subtraction_reg_a_b <= '0';
            next_carmela_sel_multiply_two_a_b <= '0';
            next_carmela_sel_reg_y_output <= '0';
            next_sm_carmela_write_enable_output <= '1';
            next_carmela_memory_double_mode <= '1';
            next_carmela_memory_only_write_mode <= '1';
            next_base_address_generator_o_increment_previous_address <= '0';
        when multiplication_direct_2 =>
            -- -- Other cases
            -- reg_a = a0_X; reg_b = b0_X; reg_acc = 0; o0_X = reg_o; operation : a*b + acc; o0_X = reg_o;
            next_sm_free_flag <= '0';
            next_sm_rotation_size <= "11";

            next_sel_address_a <= '0';
            next_sel_address_b_prime <= "00";

            next_sm_specific_carmela_address_b <= "000";

            next_carmela_sel_reg_s_reg_o_sign <= '0';

            next_carmela_sel_multiply_two_a_b <= '0';
